WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.630 --> 00:00:14.320
Create a new folder for your skin

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:48.330
Open JPOG's Data folder

00:00:49.780 --> 00:00:51.550
Open matlibs folder

00:00:55.270 --> 00:01:04.280
Select the TML file of the dino's digsite
e.g. dinos_flamingcliffs.tml

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:10.530
And copy it into the new folder

00:01:13.290 --> 00:01:24.640
Make a backup file
e.g. dinos_flamingcliffs_original.tml

00:01:36.210 --> 00:01:47.260
Copy ConvertCCT's files in the new folder

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:54.420
Drag the TML and drop it on ConvertCCT

00:02:05.320 --> 00:02:16.740
Delete useless bitmaps

00:02:20.070 --> 00:02:25.640
Open the dino skin with GIMP
e.g. Raptor.bmp, not raptor_opa

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:44.100
In GIMP modify your skin

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:54.670
Then click on File&gt;Open

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.030
Open the opacity skin
(sometimes there isn't one)

00:03:07.470 --> 00:03:10.480
Click on Select&gt;All

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:13.760
Click on Modify&gt;Copy

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:24.760
In the normal skin
make a new channel

00:03:39.890 --> 00:03:42.450
Paste the opacity skin

00:03:45.190 --> 00:03:48.490
Anchor the new level

00:03:58.250 --> 00:04:15.170
Save as Raptor.psd

00:04:17.940 --> 00:04:20.180
Close GIMP

00:04:24.970 --> 00:04:28.410
Open DDS converter 2

00:04:30.340 --> 00:04:35.160
Select Raptor.psd

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:40.140
Change Output Format to DDS

00:04:42.260 --> 00:04:43.080
Click on Options...

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.590
Choose DXT5 in DXTc format

00:04:46.470 --> 00:04:47.940
Disable Build Minimaps
Check Save alpha

00:04:48.570 --> 00:04:52.040
Click OK

00:04:55.910 --> 00:04:56.830
Click Convert

00:04:58.610 --> 00:05:00.690
And then Close

00:05:05.910 --> 00:05:10.520
Open the TML with Hex Editor Neo

00:05:32.740 --> 00:05:35.910
Click Edit&gt;Find

00:05:37.130 --> 00:05:38.940
In Type choose Hex Bytes(BYTE)

00:05:39.980 --> 00:05:42.610
In Find what write 44445320

00:05:44.100 --> 00:05:47.060
Click Find next

00:05:48.210 --> 00:05:50.450
Click on File&gt;Open

00:05:50.360 --> 00:05:52.310
(visit the link in the description
for a text guide)

00:05:51.750 --> 00:05:56.440
Open the DDS skin

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:00.960
Click Select&gt;Select All

00:06:02.220 --> 00:06:03.450
Copy

00:06:05.250 --> 00:06:07.600
Click on the TML tab

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.540
And paste

00:06:11.930 --> 00:06:14.040
Save the TML

00:06:20.940 --> 00:06:25.470
Delete the bitmaps

00:06:43.290 --> 00:06:53.920
Copy the TML into matlibs folder

00:06:58.970 --> 00:07:22.030
Make a copy of the TML and add 16
e.g. dinos_flamingcliffs16.tml

00:07:25.400 --> 00:07:30.620
now run JPOG

